<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Payment Approval Required</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <div style="background-color: #ffc107; color: #333; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
            <h1>Payment Approval Required</h1>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 20px;">
            <h2>Action Required</h2>

            <p>A payment requires your approval as a member of {{panel}}.</p>

            <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Project:</strong> {{projectName}}</p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Amount:</strong> {{paymentAmount}}</p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Panel:</strong> {{panel}}</p>
            </div>

            <p>Please review the payment details and provide your approval decision.</p>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{approvalLink}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 15px 30px; background-color: #0066cc; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">
                    Review Payment
                </a>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Important:</strong> This is part of the dual-approval workflow to ensure transparency and prevent corruption.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br>CDF Smart Hub Team</p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <p>Constituency Development Fund - Republic of Zambia</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 CDF Smart Hub. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
